    "content_toggles_kxH6e4": {
      "type": "content-toggles",
      "blocks": {
        "text_DdrRMM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What are UV DTF sticker sheets?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Custom sticker sheets offer the flexibility to feature various designs on a single sheet, allowing you to personalize the entire page and arrange the stickers in any desired layout. This customizability enhances creative freedom, enabling unique sticker placements.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_ezEtcL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I make my own sticker sheets?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>To make your own sticker sheet, you can use one of our downloadable templates and add your print-ready designs to it. Or, you can use our UV DTF gang sheet builder to create your own sticker sheet on our website.  </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_CgUR9r": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What sizes are available for your sticker sheets?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Our sticker sheets are available in a variety of sizes to suit your needs. You can choose from several dimensions, including 22 in X 6 in, 22 in X 12 in (1 ft), 22 in X 24 in (2 ft), 22 in X 60 in (5 ft), 22 in X 120 in (10 ft), and 22 in X 240 in (20 ft).</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_9xCmi8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What are UV DTF sticker sheets used for?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>UV DTF sticker sheets are used for creating custom decals and stickers with vibrant, long-lasting colors. They offer excellent adhesion on various surfaces, including laptops, water bottles, and car windows. These stickers are ideal for personalizing hard goods, and are designed to be microwave safe and waterproof.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_cfCfmV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long do sticker sheets last?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>The UV DTF Sticker Sheets are designed for durability and color retention. They are made using advanced UV DTF printing technology, which ensures the stickers remain vibrant and resistant to sunlight and extreme weather conditions. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_7daKFQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do you apply sticker sheets?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>To apply UV DTF sticker sheets, first, prepare the surface by cleaning it. Next, cut out your desired sticker and pre-squeegee it. Then, carefully separate the clear carrier sheet from the white backing. Place the sticker on the item, starting from one side to avoid bubbles and wrinkles. Finally, squeegee it again for adhesion and slowly peel off the carrier sheet.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bBpUyW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I proof my sticker sheets before purchase?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Yes, we will proof your sticker sheet before shipment. A member of the art team will thoroughly review your art, and if there are any issues, customer service will reach out to you swiftly to resolve the issue. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_aD4B7Q": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can each of my stickers on a sheet have a different shape?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Yes, each sticker on your sticker sheet can have a different and unique shape.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
